All Packages

Package Summary 
Package Description
dev.markmcd
Contains Main.java as well as /model, /view, /controller and /utils
dev.markmcd.controller
MVC controller (all program logic is here) - Controller.java is here as well as /ctl and /types
dev.markmcd.controller.ctl
CTL logic is here (in both JavaCC compilers - /Parser and /Validator) - files here are autogenerated java JavaCC - see note in readme
dev.markmcd.controller.ctl.Parser
Main CTL logic is here - files here are autogenerated by JavaCC - see note in readme
dev.markmcd.controller.ctl.Validator
The compiler here follows CTL structure, but doesn't have the CTL login (the CTL logic is in /Parser) - this is just used to check if CTL formulas are well formed (that they do not contain syntax errors)
dev.markmcd.controller.types.kripke
Custom data structures related to Kripke structures
dev.markmcd.controller.types.misc
Some miscellaneous custom data structures here
dev.markmcd.controller.types.modelCheckRelated
Custom data structures related to model checking - most of these are structures to make the passing of validation and model checking around the program easy
dev.markmcd.model
MVC model - The model is very simple and just stores the results of validation, model checking and end to end tests
dev.markmcd.utils
Some miscellaneous custom utility methods relating to Kripke structures, set operations, etc.
dev.markmcd.view
MVC view - very simple view that just prints results of validation, model checking and end to end tests to the console
